profile_positions.description:
Elicited requirements and prepare Business functional specifications for required developments/enhancements. Main responsibilities include:

• Translated business requirements into business specifications as needed; 
• Conducted JAD sessions  to present proposed solutions for business requirements to Business representatives; 
• Obtained signoff of project documentation, i.e. - Project Scope Documents to Deployment Plans; prepare test plans, specs and test data, test all allocated enhancements and new development; 	
• Provided production and user support on Discovery in-house systems (Paradigm (magic-based) and eMMS – JAVA based) as needed from identification to a resolution to communication; 
• Tracked and coordinated business requested changes; 
• I was responsible for ensuring that all enhancements on the health website were tested and signed off by the right people.
